abstract: I think of the Paul Simon song sometimes, the one that goes, 'I believe in the future we will suffer no more.  Maybe not in my lifetime, but in yours, I feel sure.'

abstract: Grand farewells (Elton John, Paul Simon), anticipated returns (Alessia Cara, Twenty One Pilots) and buzzy emerging artists (Jessie Reyez, gnash) are coming in the new season.
snippet: Grand farewells (Elton John, Paul Simon), anticipated returns (Alessia Cara, Twenty One Pilots) and buzzy emerging artists (Jessie Reyez, gnash) are coming in the new season.
lead_paragraph: This fall’s music calendar will feature farewells, anticipated returns and emerging artists. Dates are subject to change. You can listen to a playlist of songs on Spotify from the fall preview.
